contagious.Name: contagious
contagious.Description: carrying or spreading a contagious disease.

corrosive.Name: corrosive
corrosive.Description: having the quality of corroding or eating away; erosive.

ephemeral.Name: ephemeral
ephemeral.Description: lasting a very short time; short-lived; transitory.

fluffy.Name: fluffy
fluffy.Description: of, resembling, or covered with fluff.

giant.Name: giant
giant.Description: unusually large, great, or strong; gigantic; huge.

inevitable.Name: inevitable
inevitable.Description: unable to be avoided, evaded, or escaped; certain; fated.

long.Name: long
long.Description: extending, lasting, or totaling a number of specified units.

lubricated.Name: lubricated
lubricated.Description: to be slippery or smooth; to have been applied a lubricant.

martial_artist.Name: martial artist
martial_artist.Description: a master of some number of martial arts.

mending.Name: mending
mending.Description: The mending enchantment in Minecraft allows restortation of items when given XP.

parasitic.Name: parasitic
parasitic.Description: of, relating to, or characteristic of parasites.

protective.Name: protective
protective.Description: having the quality or function of protecting.

radioactive.Name: radioactive
radioactive.Description: of, pertaining to, exhibiting, or caused by radioactivity.

sharpness_III.Name: Sharpness III
sharpness_III.Description: The Sharpness enchantment in Minecraft increases damage done by swords or axes. Sharpness III adds 2.0 extra damage.

shrouded.Name: shrouded
shrouded.Description: to be covered; to be hidden from view.

slimy.Name: slimy
slimy.Description: abounding in or covered with slime.

slippery.Name: slippery
slippery.Description: tending or liable to cause slipping or sliding, as ice, oil, a wet surface, etc.

sneaky.Name: sneaky
sneaky.Description: like or suggestive of a sneak; furtive; deceitful.

stoneforged.Name: stoneforged
stoneforged.Description: to have been forged of stone.

stormblessed.Name: stormblessed
stormblessed.Description: someone who is blessed by the storm.

thick.Name: thick
thick.Description: having relatively great extent from one surface or side to the opposite; not thin.

tough.Name: tough
tough.Description: strong and durable; not easily broken or cut.

translucent.Name: translucent
translucent.Description: permitting light to pass through but diffusing it so that persons, objects, etc., on the opposite side are not clearly visible.

unbreaking_III.Name: Unbreaking III
unbreaking_III.Description: Unbreaking is an enchantment in Minecraft that gives a chance for an item's durability not to be reduced when it is used, effectively increasing the item's durability. Unbreaking II has a 33% chance of not consuming durability; on average, tools last 3 times as long.

volumnous.Name: volumnous
volumnous.Description: forming, filling, or writing a large volume or many volumes.
